
When: When Phone joins a Wi-Fi network

Automation: Run Immediately

Do:
	Get Current Location
	Get Wi-Fi network's Network Name
		Set variable SSiD to Network Details
	Current Date
		Format Date
			Date Format: Custom
			Format String: yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm a
			Locale: Default
	If Name is [Home Network Name]
		Show notification Joined [Home Network Name]
		Text
			----------------------------
			Formatted Date
			SSiD: SSiD
			Location: Current Location
			----------------------------
		Append Text to [Note Document]
	Otherwise
		Show notification Joined a network 
		Text
			----------------------------
			Formatted Date
			SSiD: SSiD
			Location: Current Location
			----------------------------
		Append Text to [Note Document]
End If 
